casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Richard Wells MOORE, Jr.
No. D-2916.
Supreme Court of the United States
July 18, 2016.
Richard Wells Moore, Jr., of Timonium, Maryland, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
